<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:126.54px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">2)  ( × ) </span><span class="cls_007">着物を</span><span class="cls_008">  </span><span class="cls_007">着るのは</span><span class="cls_008">  </span><span class="cls_007">簡単だ。</span></div>
