<div style="position:absolute;left:289.20px;top:41.34px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">じゅん  び</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:44.94px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">×</span><span class="cls_007">あした</span><span class="cls_008">  </span><span class="cls_007">会議が</span><span class="cls_008">  </span><span class="cls_007">あって、きょう</span><span class="cls_008">  </span><span class="cls_007">準備しなければ</span><span class="cls_008">  </span><span class="cls_007">なりません。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:85.74px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">２</span><span class="cls_008">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:85.80px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">名詞</span><span class="cls_012"> </span><span class="cls_006">で</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:106.14px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">這課學習的助詞「で</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:170.40px;top:106.14px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">」表示原因。這時使用的名詞中</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_007">像「じこ、じしん、か</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:126.54px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">じ等」表示自然現象、事件、發生的事情等的詞比較多。述語部分和句型</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:474.00px;top:126.54px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">1</span><span class="cls_007">一樣</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:146.94px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">有限制</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_007">不能使用含有意志的表達方式。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:82.80px;top:163.74px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">じ  しん</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:186.00px;top:163.74px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">たお</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:167.34px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">⑨</span><span class="cls_006">地震で</span><span class="cls_012">  </span><span class="cls_006">ビルが</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_006">倒れました。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:342.00px;top:169.20px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">因為地震</span><span class="cls_003">，</span><span class="cls_002">大廈倒塌了。</span></div>
