<div style="position:absolute;left:133.20px;top:184.14px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">かい  しゃ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:186.00px;top:184.14px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">やす</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:187.74px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">⑩</span><span class="cls_006">病気で</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_006">会社を</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_006">休みました。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:342.00px;top:189.60px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">因病請假沒去公司。</span></div>
