<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:4.14px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">⑯</span><span class="cls_006">マラソンの</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_006">途中で</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_006">気分が</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_006">悪く</span><span class="cls_012">  </span><span class="cls_006">なりました。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:78.00px;top:26.40px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">在馬拉松比賽的途中</span><span class="cls_003">，</span><span class="cls_002">不舒服起來。</span></div>
